<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 17 Apr 2026 01:22:03 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>随着加密货币成为主流，无许可成为一个政策问题</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-04-16/permissionless-becomes-a-policy-problem-as-crypto-goes-mainstream</link><description>进入有关加密货币监管的更广泛讨论的窗口。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/id7FmRyW24bA/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Apr 2026 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-04-16/permissionless-becomes-a-policy-problem-as-crypto-goes-mainstream</guid></item><item><title>价值 2.85 亿美元的加密货币黑客攻击和利率下降震撼了 DeFi 世界</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-16/a-285-million-crypto-hack-and-falling-yields-rock-defi-industry</link><description>去中心化金融曾经是数字资产行业最具活力的领域之一，但现在几乎面临着来自各个方面的压力。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ibO5XwxGevLY/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Apr 2026 12:15:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-16/a-285-million-crypto-hack-and-falling-yields-rock-defi-industry</guid></item><item><title>法国当局在绑架狂潮后保护加密货币高管</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-16/french-authorities-shield-crypto-execs-after-kidnapping-spree</link><description>法国当局正试图安抚紧张不安的数字资产高管和投资者，因为一系列绑架和绑架未遂事件可能会颠覆该国的加密中心雄心。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iB2kAfooVPD0/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Apr 2026 16:31:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-16/french-authorities-shield-crypto-execs-after-kidnapping-spree</guid></item><item><title>被黑的加密平台在获得新资金后将重新启动</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-16/hacked-crypto-platform-to-relaunch-after-securing-new-funding</link><description>去中心化金融平台 Drift Protocol 是本月早些时候黑客窃取了约 2.85 亿美元用户加密货币的受害者，该平台计划在从稳定币发行商 Tether Holdings SA 牵头的财团获得约 1.5 亿美元资金后重新启动。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iV_EchpB0Oc4/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Apr 2026 14:32:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-16/hacked-crypto-platform-to-relaunch-after-securing-new-funding</guid></item><item><title>AI Pivot 推动比特币矿工迈向 70% 收入里程碑</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-15/ai-pivot-pushes-bitcoin-miners-toward-a-70-revenue-milestone</link><description>那些通过挖掘比特币建立了数十亿美元业务的公司有望在今年年底前从人工智能中获得大部分收入——这是一个里程碑，标志着整个行业正在远离创造它的加密货币。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iCTlfqZu9sRo/v3/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Apr 2026 15:49:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-15/ai-pivot-pushes-bitcoin-miners-toward-a-70-revenue-milestone</guid></item><item><title>EToro 将以 7000 万美元收购加密钱包初创公司 Zengo</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-15/etoro-etor-to-acquire-crypto-wallet-startup-zengo-in-70-million-deal</link><description>EToro Group Ltd. 已同意收购加密钱包提供商 Zengo，该交易和投资平台将其业务范围扩大到去中心化金融领域。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iTsSrceD0r0I/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Apr 2026 07:30:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-15/etoro-etor-to-acquire-crypto-wallet-startup-zengo-in-70-million-deal</guid></item><item><title>法国兴业银行向数百万加密钱包用户提供美元稳定币</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-15/socgen-takes-usd-stablecoin-to-millions-of-crypto-wallet-users</link><description>法国兴业银行正在扩大其以美元计价的稳定币的覆盖范围，这是大型银行迄今为止为将数字货币带给更广泛受众而做出的最大努力之一。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i26oRrVOKUds/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Apr 2026 06:15:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-15/socgen-takes-usd-stablecoin-to-millions-of-crypto-wallet-users</guid></item></channel></rss>